系到真普選，不過得獨立調查有人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:49:16.000Z","msg":"心水清既就知其實所有野都係制度問題<br />\n唔從根本改革係唔會有用"},{"pid":"94307cd7e34abc6ca9bbfc33f6f858ca890653f9","tid":1589763,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"同意 係人都知黑警係賤 我地係時候講新野"},{"pid":"74d12118d675334125746577b90dc72d88ae6344","tid":1589763,"uid":242737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:33:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f7d10aaa47285e0820e239973e962af162a3575","tid":1589763,"uid":267983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:35:53.000Z","msg":"雖然喺香港地講「希望」好似好on9<br />\n但總好多日日都係對着何妖同班狗<br />\n<br />\n[文宣必入]Sharon Hom比左一個極重要抗爭方向大家!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1588879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1588879</a>"}]}